sacrifice on g4 or lash out with h5. } 14... Bxg4 (14... h5 15. gxh5 gxh5 (15... Nxh5 16. Nxh5 gxh5 17. Ng3 Qh4 18. Rf3 { With Bf2 coming, kicking the queen out. }) 16. Nd4 Nxd4 17. Bxd4 c5 18. e5) 15. hxg4 Nxg4 16. Qd3 Qh4 17. Rf3 { And
there's no mate. } 17... Nh2 18. Rf2 Ng4 19. e5 { Crashing through the center, not
repeating! } 19... Ncxe5 20. fxe5 Rxe5 21. Bd4 Nxf2 22. Bxf2 { Of course, we have ran
